\end_inset

 shows the CDF plot for the Kumaraswamy distribution with the parameters
 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=5$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta=1$
\end_inset

.
 The empirical CDF is shown as the grey shaded area, while the theoretical
 CDF is given by the dashed black line.
 The parameters of this distribution can be seen in the title of the generated
 plot.
\end_layout

